<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pedido Pendiente | <%= store.name %></title>
    
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/icon/favicon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500;1,600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/variables.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/brand.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/components.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    
    <main style="padding-top: 80px;">
        <section class="pending-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="pending-card">
                    <div class="pending-icon"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
                    <h1>Pedido Recibido</h1>
                    <p class="pending-subtitle">
                        Tu pedido ha sido registrado y está pendiente de pago.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="order-number">
                        <span>Número de pedido</span>
                        <strong>#<%= order.order_number %></strong>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="payment-instructions">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-credit-card me-2"></i>Instrucciones de Pago</h3>
                        
                        <div class="payment-method">
                            <h4>Transferencia Bancaria / SPEI</h4>
                            <div class="bank-details">
                                <div class="bank-row">
                                    <span>Banco:</span>
                                    <strong>BBVA México</strong>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bank-row">
                                    <span>Titular:</span>
                                    <strong>El Rincón de la Miel S.A. de C.V.</strong>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bank-row">
                                    <span>CLABE:</span>
                                    <strong>012345678901234567</strong>
                                    <button onclick="copyToClipboard('012345678901234567')" class="copy-btn"><i class="fas fa-copy"></i></button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bank-row">
                                    <span>Referencia:</span>
                                    <strong><%= order.order_number %></strong>
                                    <button onclick="copyToClipboard('<%= order.order_number %>')" class="copy-btn"><i class="fas fa-copy"></i></button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bank-row total">
                                    <span>Monto a pagar:</span>
                                    <strong>$<%= order.total ? order.total.toFixed(2) : '0.00' %> MXN</strong>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="payment-note">
                            <p><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i><strong>Importante:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Usa el número de pedido como referencia</li>
                                <li>Tu pedido se procesará al confirmar el pago</li>
                                <li>Recibirás un correo de confirmación en <strong><%= order.email %></strong></li>
                                <li>Si tienes dudas, contáctanos: <%= store.email %></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="pending-actions">
                        <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Seguir Comprando</a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">¿Necesitas Ayuda?</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    
    <script>
    function copyToClipboard(text) {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function() {
            alert('¡Copiado al portapapeles!');
        });
    }
    </script>
</body>
</html>

<style>
.pending-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
}

.pending-card {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
}

.pending-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.pending-card h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.pending-subtitle {
    color: #6B665C;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.order-number {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: #FFF8E7;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.order-number span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #9C9689;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.order-number strong {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #C4841D;
}

.payment-instructions {
    text-align: left;
    background: #FAF8F5;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.payment-instructions h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.payment-method h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #4A4640;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E8E4DB;
}

.bank-details {
    background: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.bank-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #F0EDE8;
}

.bank-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
}

.bank-row span {
    color: #9C9689;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.bank-row strong {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: #1A1A1A;
}

.bank-row.total {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    border-top: 2px solid #E8E4DB;
    border-bottom: none;
}

.bank-row.total strong {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #C4841D;
}

.copy-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
}

.copy-btn:hover {
    opacity: 1;
}

.payment-note {
    background: #FFF8E7;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.payment-note p {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: #9A6518;
}

.payment-note ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: #6B665C;
}

.payment-note li {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.pending-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
}

@media (max-width: 576px) {
    .pending-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .bank-row {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 0.25rem;
    }
}
</style>
